modules.description: Generates JUnit XML reports with typed constructs for test results, including test cases, failures, and summaries. It handles structured data such as test names, durations, and error messages. Used to produce Jenkins-compatible test reports from OUnit and Alcotest test suites.

Converts OUnit test results into JUnit-compatible test case and test suite structures. Accepts a single result or a list of results, associating them with a specified name for reporting. Generates an XML file containing the formatted test results for integration with continuous integration systems.
